title: Is We Dumb? | Didgeridoo. Oranges. Baseball Bat. Fake Owl.
description:
You ever hear the one about the dudes who decided to eat 66 pounds of oranges in 30 minutes to avoid paying extra baggage fees and then developed insanely painful mouth ulcers? It's not a joke. It's real. Let's talk about that, ramming a didgeridoo up your tailpipe, turning your uncle's skeleton into a guitar, dropping acid and rubbing glow stick liquid all over your body, and more on today's episode of Is We Dumb?!

New episodes every Wednesday at 12pm PST
